name: Bullet Master Run
summary:
It's time to get the guns out!

Do you like action spy movies? 
Then challenge yourself in an epic Bullet Master Run game! Here you must prove that you are the best spy of all! 
You are attacked by a crowd of enemies, 
eliminate them one by one but take care to not shoot the hostages! 

Future Plans:
We have an ambitious roadmap ahead to bring even more features and content to Bullet Master Run. Here’s a sneak peek at what you can expect in future updates:
